WEBVTT

00:00:28.603 --> 00:00:31.691
are not pinned down by national interests,

00:00:31.691 --> 00:00:34.528
and influence change
through citizen networks,

00:00:34.528 --> 00:00:37.084
not only state ones.

00:00:37.084 --> 00:00:41.683
And if you want to change the world,
we need more of them.

00:00:41.683 --> 00:00:44.190
But many people still ask,

00:00:44.190 --> 00:00:48.741
"Can civil society really
make a big difference?

00:00:48.741 --> 00:00:54.012
Can citizens influence and shape
national and global policy?"

00:00:54.012 --> 00:00:56.961
I never thought I would ask
myself these questions,

00:00:56.961 --> 00:01:00.211
but here I am to share some lessons